data.description: This lovely 3/2/2 home was built on a premium lot with a large back patio 10'X20' AND an additional patio extension of 10'X15' and covered pergola 10'X35'.  The lot itself has unique large side-yards which provide extra space between neighbors for more privacy!  Inside the home you will find an open concept living/kitchen and dining area with upgraded tile throughout main living/kitchen/bathrooms & halls.  The dedicated office could also be used as a 4th bdrm if desired.  This cozy charmer has upgraded ivory 42" cabinets and upgraded granite and backsplash in kitchen area.  All throughout home you will find lots of upgraded tech features such as USB wall chargers in kitchen and bath area, dedicated fiber into home, CAT6 ethernet & RG-6 coax infrastructure added throughout home w/ centralized access. Let's not forget the PEX water lines and Rheem whole-home tankless water system.  This one has it ALL!!!!!!!  Come see this one today in lovely Vanbrooke community where nature calls!
